    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Soak your<strong> skewers</strong> in <strong>cold water</strong> to prevent them from burning</p><p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice </strong>and <strong>cauliflower rice</strong> to a pot with a lid with 110ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [175ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[225ml]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once done, remove from the heat and set aside (lid on) to steam until serving</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chicken-mince-kebabs-with-green-chilli-yoghurt-and-cauli-rice/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, cut your <strong>red onion[s] </strong>into thin wedges</p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Top, tail and slice your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> into discs on the diagonal</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chicken-mince-kebabs-with-green-chilli-yoghurt-and-cauli-rice/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>green chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>garlic </strong>and <strong>parsley</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong> with your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and blitz \u2013 this is your <strong>green chilli sauce</strong></p><p>Heat the grill to very high</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chicken-mince-kebabs-with-green-chilli-yoghurt-and-cauli-rice/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine your<strong> chicken mince</strong> with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>green chilli sauce </strong>(save the rest for later!)<strong> </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>chicken kebab mixture</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chicken-mince-kebabs-with-green-chilli-yoghurt-and-cauli-rice/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Divide your <strong>chicken mixture</strong> into 2 per person and shape into long sausage shapes onto each skewer \u2013 these are your <strong>chicken skewers</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> skewers</strong> to one side of a baking tray (use tin foil to avoid mess!)</p><p>Press the <strong>chicken skewers</strong> to flatten it slightly</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Do this in batches!</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chicken-mince-kebabs-with-green-chilli-yoghurt-and-cauli-rice/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> tomato wedges</strong>, <strong>courgette discs</strong> and <strong>sliced onion</strong> to the other side of the baking tray[s]</p><p>Sprinkle over your<strong> ground coriander </strong>and season with a crack of<strong> black pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] under the grill for 12-15 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the veg has softened \u2013 these are your <strong>fragrant chicken mince kebabs & roasted veg</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chicken-mince-kebabs-with-green-chilli-yoghurt-and-cauli-rice/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the<strong> remaining green chilli sauce </strong>to your <strong>natural</strong> <strong>yoghurt</strong></p><p>Stir once or twice to swirl the <strong>green chilli sauce</strong> through the <strong>yoghurt</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>green chilli yoghurt</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/chicken-mince-kebabs-with-green-chilli-yoghurt-and-cauli-rice/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>fragrant chicken mince kebabs & roasted veg </strong>with the<strong> rice </strong>and <strong>green chilli yoghurt</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
